{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1777017916877,"sessionID":"ses_241d9f7b3ffeMqi0Lc2w61CcA3","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"apply_patch","callID":"call_eyC0AswT0rjcm4u4bH8Yrnqg","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"patchText":"*** Begin Patch\n*** Update File: D:\\agent_workspace\\capability-library\\agent-system-rules\\project-manager\\registration\\mycli\\cli.package.json\n@@\n     {\n       \"name\": \"next-update\",\n@@\n       \"entry\": \"D:\\\\agent_workspace\\\\capability-library\\\\agent-system-rules\\\\project-manager\\\\scripts\\\\project-manager.ps1\"\n     },\n+    {\n+      \"name\": \"context-add\",\n+      \"summary\": \"Add dynamic context for a project phase\",\n+      \"args\": [{\"name\": \"args\", \"required\": false, \"summary\": \"Arguments such as <id> --title <title> --phase architecture --summary <text>\", \"type\": \"string[]\"}],\n+      \"prefixArgs\": [\"context-add\"],\n+      \"entry\": \"D:\\\\agent_workspace\\\\capability-library\\\\agent-system-rules\\\\project-manager\\\\scripts\\\\project-manager.ps1\"\n+    },\n+    {\n+      \"name\": \"context-list\",\n+      \"summary\": \"List dynamic project context entries\",\n+      \"args\": [{\"name\": \"args\", \"required\": false, \"summary\": \"Arguments such as <id> [--phase architecture] [--json]\", \"type\": \"string[]\"}],\n+      \"prefixArgs\": [\"context-list\"],\n+      \"entry\": \"D:\\\\agent_workspace\\\\capability-library\\\\agent-system-rules\\\\project-manager\\\\scripts\\\\project-manager.ps1\"\n+    },\n+    {\n+      \"name\": \"context-get\",\n+      \"summary\": \"Read one dynamic project context entry\",\n+      \"args\": [{\"name\": \"args\", \"required\": false, \"summary\": \"Arguments such as <id> <context-id> [--json]\", \"type\": \"string[]\"}],\n+      \"prefixArgs\": [\"context-get\"],\n+      \"entry\": \"D:\\\\agent_workspace\\\\capability-library\\\\agent-system-rules\\\\project-manager\\\\scripts\\\\project-manager.ps1\"\n+    },\n+    {\n+      \"name\": \"current\",\n+      \"summary\": \"Show current project status, task, and next action\",\n+      \"args\": [{\"name\": \"args\", \"required\": false, \"summary\": \"Arguments such as <id> [--json]\", \"type\": \"string[]\"}],\n+      \"prefixArgs\": [\"current\"],\n+      \"entry\": \"D:\\\\agent_workspace\\\\capability-library\\\\agent-system-rules\\\\project-manager\\\\scripts\\\\project-manager.ps1\"\n+    },\n+    {\n+      \"name\": \"agent-guide\",\n+      \"summary\": \"Print project management guide and project context for agent handoff\",\n+      \"args\": [{\"name\": \"args\", \"required\": false, \"summary\": \"Arguments such as <id> [--phase validation]\", \"type\": \"string[]\"}],\n+      \"prefixArgs\": [\"agent-guide\"],\n+      \"entry\": \"D:\\\\agent_workspace\\\\capability-library\\\\agent-system-rules\\\\project-manager\\\\scripts\\\\project-manager.ps1\"\n+    },\n+    {\n+      \"name\": \"maintenance-guide\",\n+      \"summary\": \"Print maintenance and operations guide for a project\",\n+      \"args\": [{\"name\": \"args\", \"required\": false, \"summary\": \"Arguments such as <id>\", \"type\": \"string[]\"}],\n+      \"prefixArgs\": [\"maintenance-guide\"],\n+      \"entry\": \"D:\\\\agent_workspace\\\\capability-library\\\\agent-system-rules\\\\project-manager\\\\scripts\\\\project-manager.ps1\"\n+    },\n     {\n       \"name\": \"native\",\n*** Update File: D:\\agent_workspace\\capability-library\\agent-system-rules\\project-manager\\registration\\mycli\\README.md\n@@\n mycli project-manager next-add <id-or-name> --title <title>\n mycli project-manager next-update <id-or-name> <next-id> [fields]\n+mycli project-manager context-add <id-or-name> --title <title> --phase <phase>\n+mycli project-manager context-list <id-or-name> [--phase <phase>]\n+mycli project-manager context-get <id-or-name> <context-id>\n+mycli project-manager current <id-or-name>\n+mycli project-manager agent-guide <id-or-name> [--phase <phase>]\n+mycli project-manager maintenance-guide <id-or-name>\n mycli project-manager native <args...>\n@@\n mycli project-manager next-add <id> --title \"Run validation\" --type validate --set-current\n mycli project-manager next-list <id>\n mycli project-manager next-update <id> next-0001 --status done\n ```\n+\n+### Dynamic context and agent handoff\n+\n+Use dynamic context to record stage-specific assumptions, requirements, feasibility findings, architecture notes, validation results, operation notes, and maintenance rules.\n+\n+```powershell\n+mycli project-manager context-add <id> --title \"Architecture decision context\" --phase architecture --type architecture --summary \"Use file-based registry first\" --file README.md --tag registry\n+mycli project-manager context-list <id> --phase architecture\n+mycli project-manager context-get <id> context-0001\n+```\n+\n+When an agent team takes over a project, start with:\n+\n+```powershell\n+mycli project-manager current <id>\n+mycli project-manager agent-guide <id>\n+mycli project-manager agent-guide <id> --phase validation\n+mycli project-manager maintenance-guide <id>\n+```\n+\n+`agent-guide` prints project management rules, current status, open tasks, open next actions, and dynamic context for the requested phase.\n*** Update File: D:\\agent_workspace\\capability-library\\agent-system-rules\\project-manager\\README.md\n@@\n mycli project-manager next-list <id-or-name>\n mycli project-manager next-add <id-or-name> --title <title>\n mycli project-manager next-update <id-or-name> <next-id> [fields]\n+mycli project-manager context-add <id-or-name> --title <title> --phase <phase>\n+mycli project-manager context-list <id-or-name> [--phase <phase>]\n+mycli project-manager context-get <id-or-name> <context-id>\n+mycli project-manager current <id-or-name>\n+mycli project-manager agent-guide <id-or-name> [--phase <phase>]\n+mycli project-manager maintenance-guide <id-or-name>\n ```\n@@\n ### 7.6 next-action 命令\n@@\n .agent-project/next-actions/next-0001.json\n ```\n+\n+### 7.7 动态上下文命令\n+\n+动态上下文用于接收项目各阶段持续补充的信息，例如：\n+\n+- 需求设计中的用户偏好和边界；\n+- 可行性分析中的风险和结论；\n+- 架构设计中的取舍；\n+- 施工中的实现注意事项；\n+- 验证中的测试发现；\n+- 持续运行中的运行记录和异常；\n+- 维护中的修复准则。\n+\n+```powershell\n+mycli project-manager context-add project-manager --title \"Architecture context\" --phase architecture --type architecture --summary \"Use project.json as truth and registry as cache.\" --file README.md --tag registry\n+mycli project-manager context-list project-manager --phase architecture\n+mycli project-manager context-get project-manager context-0001\n+```\n+\n+动态上下文存储在：\n+\n+```text\n+.agent-project/context/entries/context-0001.json\n+```\n+\n+### 7.8 agent 接手命令\n+\n+当 agent 团队接手项目时，优先运行：\n+\n+```powershell\n+mycli project-manager current project-manager\n+mycli project-manager agent-guide project-manager\n+mycli project-manager agent-guide project-manager --phase validation\n+mycli project-manager maintenance-guide project-manager\n+```\n+\n+其中：\n+\n+- `current` 输出当前项目状态、当前 task、当前 next-action。\n+- `agent-guide` 输出项目管理准则、当前状态、开放任务、开放推进项和阶段动态上下文。\n+- `maintenance-guide` 输出维护规则和 operations 快照。\n@@\n mycli project-manager get project-manager\n+mycli project-manager current project-manager\n+mycli project-manager agent-guide project-manager\n ```\n*** Update File: D:\\agent_workspace\\capability-library\\agent-system-rules\\project-manager\\SKILL.md\n@@\n mycli project-manager next-update <id> next-0001 --status done\n+mycli project-manager context-add <id> --title \"Validation finding\" --phase validation --summary \"...\"\n+mycli project-manager current <id>\n+mycli project-manager agent-guide <id>\n+mycli project-manager maintenance-guide <id>\n ```\n@@\n - Use `activity=degraded` when an ongoing project still runs but has partial failures or quality degradation.\n - Use `attention[]` for user/agent queues such as `needs_user_decision`, `needs_validation`, or `needs_maintenance`.\n+\n+## Dynamic Context and Agent Takeover\n+\n+Use dynamic context commands to capture changing project context by phase:\n+\n+```powershell\n+mycli project-manager context-add <project> --title \"Requirement boundary\" --phase requirements --type requirement --summary \"...\"\n+mycli project-manager context-add <project> --title \"Architecture note\" --phase architecture --type architecture --summary \"...\" --file README.md\n+mycli project-manager context-list <project> --phase validation\n+mycli project-manager context-get <project> context-0001\n+```\n+\n+When an agent team takes over a project, use:\n+\n+```powershell\n+mycli project-manager current <project>\n+mycli project-manager agent-guide <project>\n+mycli project-manager agent-guide <project> --phase <phase>\n+mycli project-manager maintenance-guide <project>\n+```\n+\n+`agent-guide` is the primary handoff surface. It includes project identity, management rules, maintenance rules, current status, open tasks, open next actions, and phase-specific dynamic context.\n*** End Patch"},"output":"Success. Updated the following files:\nM agent_workspace/capability-library/agent-system-rules/project-manager/registration/mycli/cli.package.json\nM agent_workspace/capability-library/agent-system-rules/project-manager/registration/mycli/README.md\nM agent_workspace/capability-library/agent-system-rules/project-manager/README.md\nM agent_workspace/capability-library/agent-system-rules/project-manager/SKILL.md","metadata":{"diff":"Index: D:\\agent_workspace\\capability-library\\agent-system-rules\\project-manager\\registration\\mycli\\cli.package.json\n===================================================================\n--- D:\\agent_workspace\\capability-library\\agent-system-rules\\project-manager\\registration\\mycli\\cli.package.json\n+++ D:\\agent_workspace\\capability-library\\agent-system-rules\\project-manager\\registration\\mycli\\cli.package.json\n@@ -199,8 +199,50 @@\n   \"prefixArgs\": [\"next-update\"],\n   \"entry\": \"D:\\\\agent_workspace\\\\capability-library\\\\agent-system-rules