{"type":"text","timestamp":1777018007124,"sessionID":"ses_241d9f7b3ffeMqi0Lc2w61CcA3","part":{"id":"prt_dbe869452001HIQ73ak00cvIun","messageID":"msg_dbe865a86001VJTl5xtXHtaIQM","sessionID":"ses_241d9f7b3ffeMqi0Lc2w61CcA3","type":"text","text":"已补完，并且通过 `mycli project-manager` 暴露出来了。现在它不只是项目注册/查询工具，也可以作为 **agent 团队接手项目时的项目上下文入口**。\n\n## 新增能力\n\n### 1. 动态上下文补全\n\n现在每个项目可以按阶段持续补充上下文：\n\n```text\n.agent-project/context/entries/context-0001.json\n```\n\n适合记录：\n\n- 需求阶段：用户偏好、范围、边界；\n- 可行性阶段：风险、调研结论；\n- 架构阶段：架构取舍、依赖、约束；\n- 施工阶段：实现注意事项；\n- 验证阶段：测试发现、验收标准；\n- 运行阶段：运行记录、异常模式；\n- 维护阶段：修复准则、维护注意事项。\n\n命令：\n\n```powershell\nmycli project-manager context-add <project> --title <title> --phase <phase> --summary <text>\nmycli project-manager context-list <project> [--phase <phase>]\nmycli project-manager context-get <project> <context-id>\n```\n\n示例：\n\n```powershell\nmycli project-manager context-add project-manager `\n  --title \"Agent takeover context\" `\n  --phase delivery `\n  --type handoff `\n  --priority high `\n  --summary \"Agent teams should start with current, agent-guide, task-list, next-list, and status before modifying this project.\" `\n  --file README.md `\n  --file SKILL.md `\n  --tag handoff `\n  --tag guide\n```\n\n---\n\n### 2. 当前项目快照\n\n新增：\n\n```powershell\nmycli project-manager current <project>\n```\n\n它会输出：\n\n- 当前生命周期；\n- 当前阶段；\n- 当前活动状态；\n- health / delivery / attention；\n- current summary；\n- 当前 task；\n- 当前 next-action。\n\n支持 JSON：\n\n```powershell\nmycli project-manager current <project> --json\n```\n\n---\n\n### 3. agent 团队接手指南\n\n新增：\n\n```powershell\nmycli project-manager agent-guide <project>\nmycli project-manager agent-guide <project> --phase validation\n```\n\n它会输出一份 agent 接手项目的说明，包括：\n\n- 项目身份；\n- 当前状态；\n- 当前 focus；\n- 项目管理准则；\n- 维护准则；\n- open tasks；\n- open next-actions；\n- 指定阶段的动态上下文。\n\n这就是后续 agent 团队接手项目时的入口命令。\n\n建议接手项目第一步执行：\n\n```powershell\nmycli project-manager current <project>\nmycli project-manager agent-guide <project>\nmycli project-manager status <project>\nmycli project-manager task-list <project>\nmycli project-manager next-list <project>\n```\n\n---\n\n### 4. 维护准则入口\n\n新增：\n\n```powershell\nmycli project-manager maintenance-guide <project>\n```\n\n它会输出：\n\n- agent handoff guide；\n- maintenance phase 相关动态上下文；\n- operations / maintenance snapshot；\n- ongoing 项目的运行信息；\n- finite 项目则提示 operations not configured。\n\n---\n\n## 已同步到 help / skill\n\n我更新并同步了：\n\n```text\nD:\\agent_workspace\\capability-library\\agent-system-rules\\project-manager\\README.md\nD:\\agent_workspace\\capability-library\\agent-system-rules\\project-manager\\SKILL.md\nD:\\agent_workspace\\capability-library\\agent-system-rules\\project-manager\\registration\\mycli\\README.md\nD:\\agent_workspace\\capability-library\\agent-system-rules\\project-manager\\registration\\mycli\\cli.package.json\n```\n\n并执行了：\n\n```powershell\nD:\\agent_workspace\\capability-library\\agent-system-rules\\project-manager\\scripts\\register-to-mycli.ps1\n```\n\n所以现在：\n\n```powershell\nmycli project-manager --help\nmycli project-manager list\nmycli skill-library search project-manager\n```\n\n都能看到新能力。\n\n---\n\n## 新增命令清单\n\n现在 `mycli project-manager list` 里已经有：\n\n```text\ncontext-add\ncontext-list\ncontext-get\ncurrent\nagent-guide\nmaintenance-guide\n```\n\n加上已有的：\n\n```text\ninit\nregister\nscan\nrefresh\nlist\nquery\nget\nstatus\nupdate-status\ntask-list\ntask-add\ntask-update\nnext-list\nnext-add\nnext-update\n```\n\n---\n\n## 验证通过\n\n我已经验证：\n\n```powershell\npython -m py_compile D:\\agent_workspace\\capability-library\\agent-system-rules\\project-manager\\src\\project_manager.py\n```\n\n通过。\n\n验证动态上下文：\n\n```powershell\nmycli project-manager context-add project-manager ...\nmycli project-manager context-list project-manager --phase delivery\n```\n\n通过。\n\n验证当前项目快照：\n\n```powershell\nmycli project-manager current project-manager\n```\n\n通过。\n\n验证 agent 接手指南：\n\n```powershell\nmycli project-manager agent-guide project-manager --phase delivery\n```\n\n通过。\n\n验证维护准则：\n\n```powershell\nmycli project-manager maintenance-guide project-manager\n```\n\n通过。\n\n---\n\n## 当前 project-manager 状态\n\n已经更新为：\n\n```text\nlifecycle: active\nphase: delivery\nactivity: stable\nhealth: green\ndelivery: published\nsummary: Project-manager now supports dynamic phase context, current project snapshots, agent handoff guides, and maintenance guides via mycli.\n```\n\n现在已经能满足你说的：\n\n> 接受项目各个阶段的动态上下文补全  \n> agent 团队接手项目之后可以通过命令获取项目管理准则、项目相关信息、维护准则等\n\n以后接手任何项目，标准入口就是：\n\n```powershell\nmycli project-manager current <project>\nmycli project-manager agent-guide <project>\nmycli project-manager maintenance-guide <project>\n```","time":{"start":1777017984082,"end":1777018007121}}}
